<br />\n何況所謂中國一系列攪事<br />\n大多數都係香港人高官自己沖去奶鞋底"},{"pid":"fa4ff82de6ee35899d68d34a3ce9fb936a48bf3b","tid":276722,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"唔好激嬲共慘黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade00efd9fbce6455fd9a1991b04fd5283ee5ae1","tid":276722,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"當年以色列立國，都好似今日班恐怖份子"},{"pid":"bbb5e714fedb3c924df75a1aa89a3138b10902fc","tid":276722,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74b726a7ebb68afbecfd7616cae9eee983125d7b","tid":276722,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6091c97353d3b35b2c9985cfd998ec0332cf13","tid":276722,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"星馬分家就係避免流血<br />\n<br />\n想流血既人, 先會反對港獨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/201507/20150710/1895_-_10_10_2008.jpg?itok=zeEwwSib\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F201507%2F20150710%2F1895_-_10_10_2008.jpg%3Fitok%3DzeEwwSib&h=66823d4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"357a5b06b8f68053b3eb2d48331bdad2f4befbb2","tid":276722,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edae434f940752c8a9664d86e0275e278522baaf","tid":276722,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"1965年8月10日，新加坡歷史最悠久《海峽時報》的頭條，就是新馬分家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.read01.com/uploads/0DJ1MY01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0DJ1MY01.jpg&h=d923901f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{